			</item>
			<item>
				<title>AI相关观点两则</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/ai%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 19:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/ai%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;转载自&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDc2MjQxMg==&amp;amp;mid=2247494796&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=061de8911ac656b90988a26cc3f0c0bc&amp;amp;poc_token=HPVbVGqjpXaHCSOFp088zx8YCzmp5nwbJkQUdjmN&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;深思圈&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;ai-开发的三个阶段你现在在哪里&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI 开发的三个阶段：你现在在哪里&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#ai-%e5%bc%80%e5%8f%91%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%aa%e9%98%b6%e6%ae%b5%e4%bd%a0%e7%8e%b0%e5%9c%a8%e5%9c%a8%e5%93%aa%e9%87%8c&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kash 一开场就画了一条清晰的线：软件开发的 AI 化，正在经历三个阶段的演进。理解自己在哪个阶段，是判断下一步该怎么做的前提。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>消费者只喜欢消磨时间</title>
				<link>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AA%E5%96%9C%E6%AC%A2%E6%B6%88%E7%A3%A8%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
